@startuml
title GenClaw 顺序架构图

top to bottom direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam ArrowColor #475569
skinparam component {
  BorderColor #334155
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
}
skinparam database {
  BorderColor #92400E
  BackgroundColor #FFF7ED
}
skinparam cloud {
  BorderColor #1D4ED8
  BackgroundColor #EFF6FF
}

actor "用户" as User

component "1. CLI 入口\n接收 prompt / 命令\n文件: genclaw/cli.py" as CLI
component "2. 编排层\n创建运行状态, 调度各阶段\n文件: genclaw/pipeline.py" as Pipeline
component "3. 认知层\n理解需求, 生成 CanvasPlan\n目录: genclaw/agent" as Agent
component "4. 可选检索\n补充知识事实\n文件: genclaw/search.py" as Search
component "5. 代码画布层\nCanvasPlan -> canvas.* -> sketch.png\n目录: genclaw/renderers" as Renderer
component "6. 图像生成层\n以 sketch 为条件生成 final.png\n目录: genclaw/generators" as Generator
component "7. 审查层\n检查结构与最终图像\n目录: genclaw/review" as Reviewer
database "8. 运行产物\noutputs/runs/<run-id>/\nrequest.json / plan.json / canvas.*\nsketch.png / final.png / review.json / trace.jsonl" as Artifacts

User --> CLI : 输入需求
CLI --> Pipeline : 启动 run
Pipeline --> Agent : conceptualize
Agent --> Search : 知识类任务
Search --> Renderer : 带知识的 CanvasPlan
Agent --> Renderer : 普通任务的 CanvasPlan
Renderer --> Generator : sketch.png
Generator --> Reviewer : final.png
Reviewer --> Artifacts : 写入审查与最终产物

note right of Agent
  CanvasPlan 是核心契约:
  后续渲染和审查都围绕它执行。
end note

note right of Generator
  外部服务只出现在相关阶段:
  LLM 用于认知层,VLM 用于审查层,
  图像模型用于生成层,Search 用于检索层。
end note

note right of Reviewer
  审查不通过且仍有预算时,
  编排层会进入 revise 后重新渲染。
end note

@enduml
